---
import ProductLayout from '@/layouts/ProductLayout.astro';
---

<ProductLayout
  title="BSage — Ontology-Based Knowledge Management"
  description="Remembers and connects — no organizing needed."
  locale="en"
  product="BSage"
  accent="#10b981"
  appUrl="https://sage.bsvibe.dev"
>
  <h1>BSage</h1>
  <p class="product-tagline">Remembers and connects — no organizing needed. AI structures your knowledge and surfaces the right information at the right moment.</p>

  <h2>Key Features</h2>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Ontology Linking</h3>
      <p>Automatically discovers relationships between concepts. Scattered information becomes a meaningful knowledge map.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Semantic Search</h3>
      <p>Search by meaning, not keywords. Find "cost reduction discussions" and get results about "budget", "ROI", and "optimization" too.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>Auto-Organization</h3>
      <p>Just save it. AI handles tagging, categorization, and linking automatically. Stop spending time on organizing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>AI Summaries</h3>
      <p>Long documents, meeting notes, conversations — distilled to key points. Grasp context quickly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>From Personal Assistant to Org Platform</h2>
  <p>BSage starts as personal knowledge management but scales to a team-wide knowledge platform. Onboarding, project history, decision context — organizational knowledge never gets lost.</p>

  <h2>Use Cases</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Research</strong> — Connect papers, articles, and notes to discover new insights</li>
    <li><strong>PMs</strong> — Auto-record project history and decision-making context</li>
    <li><strong>Team Leads</strong> — Team knowledge sharing, onboarding automation, knowledge preservation</li>
    <li><strong>Individuals</strong> — A second brain connecting reading notes, learning memos, and ideas</li>
  </ul>
</ProductLayout>
